msg: The changes made to ControlBean.vm and ControlMacro.vm in r124238 was to accomodate IDE (such as Eclipse 3.1Mx)
that are not fully JDK5 compliant.  I have limited the changes to ControlBean.vm only and reverted any changes
made in ControlMacros.vm, so only one file will need to be reverted when this is no longer required.  I have also
commented on how to remove this change in the code.
